'''古賽爾戰役'''（'''Al-Qusayr offensive'''）是開始於2013年4月4日，由敘利亞政府軍和[[真主黨|真主黨]]所發動的戰役，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/jordan-arrests-8-syrian-refugees-suspected-of-inciting-camp-riots-in-troubled-camp/2013/04/21/7a06a3c0-aa5a-11e2-9e1c-bb0fb0c2edd9_story.html |title=Syrian opposition calls on Hezbollah to stay out of Syria’s civil war |access-date=2013-04-26 |archive-date=2019-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205060928/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/jordan-arrests-8-syrian-refugees-suspected-of-inciting-camp-riots-in-troubled-camp/2013/04/21/7a06a3c0-aa5a-11e2-9e1c-bb0fb0c2edd9_story.html }}</ref> 目標攻佔古賽爾附近被敘利亞反對派佔領的所有村莊，使[[古賽爾_(敘利亞)|古賽爾]]逐漸陷入包圍，進而攻打。<ref name="shield">{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/21/Activists-Syrian-regime-provides-Hezbollah-aerial-shield-in-Qusayr-.html |title=Activists: Syrian regime provides Hezbollah aerial shield in Qusayr |access-date=2013-04-26 |archive-date=2020-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011224241/https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/21/Activists-Syrian-regime-provides-Hezbollah-aerial-shield-in-Qusayr-.html }}</ref>另外，此地區也是[[霍姆斯戰役|霍姆斯戰役]]中重要的補給運輸路線。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/04/21/us-syria-crisis-lebanon-idUSBRE93K0DN20130421 |title=Syria fighting flares both sides of Lebanese border |access-date=2013-05-05 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924180737/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/04/21/us-syria-crisis-lebanon-idUSBRE93K0DN20130421 }}</ref>

== 背景 ==
自從2011年11月起，[[古賽爾_(敘利亞)|古賽爾]]持續地遭到敘利亞政府軍圍攻，直到2012年2月大規模戰鬥前為止，統計共有66名居民喪生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/gallery/2012/feb/01/syria-arab-and-middle-east-protests#/?picture=385333879&index=0 |title=On the Syrian frontline in al-Qusayr -in pictures |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2013-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130428072234/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/gallery/2012/feb/01/syria-arab-and-middle-east-protests#/?picture=385333879&index=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此城市的重要性在於位在與[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]的邊境附近，可作為軍用武器的走私路線，<ref name="rt527">{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/op-edge/syria-israel-iran-ali-527/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2014-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140829101522/http://rt.com/op-edge/syria-israel-iran-ali-527/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>象徵著邊界的掌控權。<ref name="rt550">{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/qusair-strategic-syria-rebels-550/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2014-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815211927/http://rt.com/news/qusair-strategic-syria-rebels-550/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>更重要的是，此處為[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]與[[霍姆斯_(敘利亞)|霍姆斯]]之間高速公路的必經之地。對於政府軍而言，攻下此城將可切斷反對派的補給路線，迫使於霍姆斯作戰的反對派撤守。另外，此處也能通往[[阿拉維派|阿拉維派]]的重鎮[[塔尔图斯|塔尔图斯]]（Tartous）。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22595767 |title=Syria conflict: Qusair's strategic importance |work=BBC News |date=2013-06-05 |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2013-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224203212/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22595767 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 戰鬥 ==
=== 邊界衝突 ===
4月11日，政府軍與[[真主黨|真主黨]]聯手，奪取位於山頭的戰略要地泰爾艾納比曼度（Tell al-Nabi Mando），戰鬥持續至隔天仍有零星的衝突。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cp24.com/world/syrian-troops-battle-rebels-in-hills-near-lebanon-1.1234863 |title=Syrian troops battle rebels in hills near Lebanon |access-date=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427114541/https://www.cp24.com/world/syrian-troops-battle-rebels-in-hills-near-lebanon-1.1234863 }}</ref>據報導，40名真主黨民兵和政府軍在激戰中陣亡。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/13/Activists-say-40-Hezbollah-Syrian-regime-fighters-killed-in-Qusayr-clashes.html |title=Activists say 40 Hezbollah, Syrian regime fighters killed in Qusayr clashes |access-date=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210060641/https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/13/Activists-say-40-Hezbollah-Syrian-regime-fighters-killed-in-Qusayr-clashes.html }}</ref><ref name="closesin"/>泰爾艾納比曼度的軍事重要性在於位置，控制此地就可向邊境地區的大部分村莊攻擊，因此先前附近親政府的村莊居民於反對派攻下山頭後紛紛逃離。<ref name="threatened">{{Cite web |url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/security/2013/04/syrian-conflict-battles-strategic-lebanon.html |title=Northern Bekaa Villages Threatened by Syria War |access-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025173524/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/security/2013/04/syrian-conflict-battles-strategic-lebanon.html |archive-date=2014-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

4月14日，為了報復真主黨，而對[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]警告之後，反對派進行火箭攻擊，黎巴嫩的村莊赫美爾（Hermel）、艾卡薩（al-Qasr）先後遭到打擊，使得兩人喪生，其中一人為孩童，<ref name="threatened"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/nownews/fire-from-syria-kills-two-in-lebanon |title=Fire from Syria kills two in Lebanon |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019081742/https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/nownews/fire-from-syria-kills-two-in-lebanon |dead-url=no }}</ref>而有六人受傷。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ansamed.info/ansamed/en/news/nations/syria/2013/04/15/Syrian-regime-rockets-kill-least-2-Lebanon_8557418.html |title=Syrian regime rockets kill at least 2 in Lebanon |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025152858/http://www.ansamed.info/ansamed/en/news/nations/syria/2013/04/15/Syrian-regime-rockets-kill-least-2-Lebanon_8557418.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

4月17日，政府軍對艾布未達艾沙克雅（al-Buwaydah al-Sharqiyah）轟炸，造成至少12人死亡，包括兩名女性和兩名小孩。同時，阿比爾（Abil）外圍的戰鬥也持續進行中，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://al-shorfa.com/en_GB/articles/meii/newsbriefs/2013/04/17/newsbrief-01 |title=Syrian regime bombardment kills 12 in Homs village |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2013-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530044517/http://al-shorfa.com/en_GB/articles/meii/newsbriefs/2013/04/17/newsbrief-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 反對派表示，在古賽爾附近的艾尼薩里耶（al-Nazariyeh）有700名真主黨民兵駐紮。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2013/04/17/hezbollah-deploys-700-fighters-in-syrias-homs-report/ |title=Hezbollah deploys 700 fighters in Syria’s Homs, report |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027141721/https://yalibnan.com/2013/04/17/hezbollah-deploys-700-fighters-in-syrias-homs-report/ }}</ref>

4月18日，反對派控制了古賽爾附近的艾達巴（al-Dab'a）空軍基地，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.news.com.au/breaking-news/world/syria-rebels-claim-strategic-airbase/story-e6frfkui-1226623878591 |title=Syria rebels claim strategic airbase |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2013-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731095637/http://www.news.com.au/breaking-news/world/syria-rebels-claim-strategic-airbase/story-e6frfkui-1226623878591 |dead-url=no }}</ref>此基地當時並無停放飛機，主要由地面部隊進駐。另一方面，政府軍攻下了阿比爾，造成21名反對派方士兵陣亡，其中包括一名指揮官。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/index.php?option=com_news&nid=5304&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UXSmHLVHJCh |title=About 160 people were killed yesterday |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2014-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023033535/http://www.syriahr.com/index.php?option=com_news&nid=5304&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UXSmHLVHJCh |dead-url=no }}</ref>敘利亞人權觀察團（SOHR）的人士表示，政府軍掌控阿比爾後得以阻礙反對派於古賽爾與荷姆斯的聯繫，雖然攻下空軍基地有助於減輕對反對派的攻擊，但阿比爾的陷落讓局勢更加複雜。<ref name="seize">{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/130418/syria-troops-seize-strategic-homs-village |title=Syria troops seize strategic Homs village |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2013-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101234454/http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/130418/syria-troops-seize-strategic-homs-village |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2013/4/18/syria-live-assad-no-to-surrender-no-to-submission.html |title=Syria Live: Assad "No to Surrender, No to Submission" |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2017-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009212620/http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2013/4/18/syria-live-assad-no-to-surrender-no-to-submission.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

4月20日，政府軍和真主黨攻占拉旺尼耶（Radwaniyeh），加緊對古賽爾的包圍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/Dozens-killed-in-battle-near-Damascus-Watchdog/articleshow/19650952.cms |title=Dozens killed in battle near Damascus: Watchdog |accessdate=2013-06-15 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615215923/timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/Dozens-killed-in-battle-near-Damascus-Watchdog/articleshow/19650952.cms? |dead-url=no }}</ref>反對派人士表示，政府軍和真主黨的配合十分堅強，真主黨民兵於前進時還有空中的支援。真主黨同時攻擊了布罕尼亞（Burhaniya），泰爾艾納比曼度、沙科賈（Saqraja）和阿布赫里（Abu Huri）也傳出發生戰鬥的消息。另一名反對派人士表示，情勢已轉變得相當危急，政府軍試圖控制邊境地區，進而攻陷古賽爾。<ref name="shield">[http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/21/Activists-Syrian-regime-provides-Hezbollah-aerial-shield-in-Qusayr-.html Activists: Syrian regime provides Hezbollah aerial shield in Qusayr]</ref>

4月21日，布罕尼亞、沙科賈宣告落入政府軍手中，代表政府軍可沿黎敘邊界的[[奧龍特斯河|奧龍特斯河]]前往古賽爾西方。同時間，赫美爾與艾卡薩再度遭遇反對派的火箭襲擊，繼續報復真主黨的進攻行動。<!-- <ref name="Reuters" /> --><ref name="closesin">{{Cite web |url=http://www.france24.com/en/20130421-syria-army-closes-qusayr-near-lebanon |title=Syria army closes in on Qusayr near Lebanon |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2013-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514044805/http://www.france24.com/en/20130421-syria-army-closes-qusayr-near-lebanon |dead-url=no }}</ref>此時，也象徵有八個村莊進入政府軍的掌控，而真主黨則從[[貝卡谷地|貝卡谷地]]推進至古賽爾，與政府軍由霍姆斯向南配合，形成鉗形攻勢。<ref name="mired">{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/thomson-reuters/130421/lebanon-border-area-mired-syrian-conflict |title=Lebanon border area mired in Syrian conflict |accessdate=2013-04-26 |archive-date=2013-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510082727/http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/thomson-reuters/130421/lebanon-border-area-mired-syrian-conflict |dead-url=no }}</ref>

4月22日，反對派與真主黨持續於古賽爾附近的村莊戰鬥，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2013/04/22/hezbollahs-elite-leading-the-battle-in-qusayr-region-of-syria/ |title=Hezbollah’s elite leading the battle in Qusayr region of Syria |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2016-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317030857/http://yalibnan.com/2013/04/22/hezbollahs-elite-leading-the-battle-in-qusayr-region-of-syria/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>反對派宣稱有18名真主黨民兵在此次戰鬥中陣亡，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/23/Free-Syrian-Army-kills-18-Hezbollah-fighters-in-Syrian-city-of-Qusayr.html |title=FSA reportedly kills 18 Hezbollah fighters in Syrian city of Qusayr |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427114649/https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/23/Free-Syrian-Army-kills-18-Hezbollah-fighters-in-Syrian-city-of-Qusayr.html }}</ref>而指揮官則表示已收復阿布赫里和艾莫（Al-Mouh），但此消息未被第三方所證實。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/nownews/hezbollah-attempt-to-storm-homs-suburbs-foiled-by-rebels |title=Rebels say foiled Hezbollah attacks in Homs |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019082200/https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/nownews/hezbollah-attempt-to-storm-homs-suburbs-foiled-by-rebels }}</ref>

4月23日，反對派發射更多的火箭攻擊赫美爾。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.france24.com/en/20130423-qusayr-battle-pits-syria-rebels-against-army-hezbollah |title=Qusayr battle pits Syria rebels against army, Hezbollah |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2013-06-30 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130630210729/http://www.france24.com/en/20130423-qusayr-battle-pits-syria-rebels-against-army-hezbollah |dead-url=yes }}</ref>此外，政府軍人士認為古賽爾「頂多剩下幾天」，該城即將易主。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.brecorder.com/top-news/108-pakistan-top-news/116591-syria-chemical-weapons-fears-fierce-clashes-near-homs.html |title=Syria chemical weapons fears, fierce clashes near Homs |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2015-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119070644/http://www.brecorder.com/top-news/108-pakistan-top-news/116591-syria-chemical-weapons-fears-fierce-clashes-near-homs.html }}</ref>

4月24日，戰鬥轉移到古賽爾西北的安艾坦奴爾（Ayn al-Tannur），政府軍則在奧龍特斯河西岸的村莊駐紮，等待重整加強後往古賽爾前進。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-national-defense-forces-forefront-qusayr-fighting |title=Syria: National Defense Forces at Forefront of Qusayr Fighting |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025154044/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-national-defense-forces-forefront-qusayr-fighting |archive-date=2014-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

4月26日，根據SOHR表示，從霍姆斯到海岸發生大規模衝突。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lorientlejour.com/article/811967/bataille-acharnee-a-damas-nombre-record-de-raids-de-laviation.html |title=Bataille acharnée à Damas, nombre record de raids de l'aviation |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008030519/https://www.lorientlejour.com/article/811967/bataille-acharnee-a-damas-nombre-record-de-raids-de-laviation.html }}</ref>另外，反對派鎖定目標，攻打霍姆斯和古賽爾之間的村莊卡曼（Kamam）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2013/4/26/syria-today-the-debate-over-chemical-weapons.html#1811 |title=Syria Today: The Debate Over Chemical Weapons |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126114746/http://www.enduringamerica.com/home/2013/4/26/syria-today-the-debate-over-chemical-weapons.html#1811 }}</ref>

4月29日，六枚火箭襲擊貝卡谷地的村莊瑪查理艾奎（Macharih el-Qaa），造成一人受傷。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lorientlejour.com/article/812320/liban-six-obus-syriens-sabattent-sur-macharih-el-qaa-dans-la-bekaa.html |title=Liban : six obus syriens s'abattent sur Macharih el-Qaa dans la Békaa |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008152226/https://www.lorientlejour.com/article/812320/liban-six-obus-syriens-sabattent-sur-macharih-el-qaa-dans-la-bekaa.html }}</ref>

5月2日，戰火延燒至邊境村莊祖西亞（Jusiya），反對派和政府軍、親政府民兵、真主黨成員進行戰鬥。{{citation needed|date=2013年6月}}

5月4日，根據SOHR表示，古賽爾外圍的果園地區也發生戰鬥，並且古賽爾多處遭受轟炸，造成反對派五人陣亡，包括一名指揮官。真主黨的精銳部隊也參與了此次戰事，先前此批民兵攻下了許多附近的村莊。{{citation needed|date=2013年6月}}

5月5日，古賽爾的城邊發生衝突並且遭到轟炸，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lorientlejour.com/article/813088/le-commandant-de-laeroport-militaire-syrien-de-mennegh-tue.html |title=Le commandant de l'aéroport militaire syrien de Mennegh tué |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010083732/https://www.lorientlejour.com/article/813088/le-commandant-de-laeroport-militaire-syrien-de-mennegh-tue.html }}</ref>而反對派要求增援。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/05/05/FSA-brigade-pledges-to-fight-Hezbollah-s-Qusayr-advances.html |title=FSA brigade pledges to fight Hezbollah's Qusayr advances |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009020633/https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/05/05/FSA-brigade-pledges-to-fight-Hezbollah-s-Qusayr-advances.html }}</ref>[[伊朗|伊朗]]媒體[[Press_TV|Press TV]]報導政府軍已經奪取東邊最後的主要據點泰哈那許（Tal Hanash），完成對古賽爾的包圍網。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/05/04/301829/syrian-army-gains-control-of-strategic-qusayr-suburban-areas/ |title=Syrian Army gains control of strategic Qusayr Suburban areas |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924132713/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/05/04/301829/syrian-army-gains-control-of-strategic-qusayr-suburban-areas/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

5月6日，城邊村莊艾斯洛米亞（al-Sloumiya）陷入戰火<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://supportkurds.org/news/monday-6-may-2013/ |title=Monday 6 May 2013 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615215920/http://supportkurds.org/news/monday-6-may-2013/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而反對派的一枚火箭落在艾卡薩，其他六枚則攻擊達巴比亞（Dabbabiya）和諾拉（Noura）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lorientlejour.com/article/813126/plusieurs-obus-tires-de-syrie-sabattent-au-liban.html |title=<nowiki>Plusieurs obus tirés de Syrie s’abattent au Liban</nowiki> |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009152501/https://www.lorientlejour.com/article/813126/plusieurs-obus-tires-de-syrie-sabattent-au-liban.html }}</ref>。另外，古賽爾城外的戰鬥進入第二天後依舊持續。<ref name="ease">{{Cite web |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887323687604578466960418934802.html |title=Hezbollah Steps Up in Syria as Israel Tries to Ease Tension |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2013-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722133521/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887323687604578466960418934802.html }}</ref>

5月7日，反對派表示經過喪失周圍村莊後，他們恐怕會失去古賽爾。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/08/world/middleeast/hezbollah-takes-risks-by-fighting-rebels-in-syria.html?_r=0 |title=Hezbollah Takes Risks by Fighting Rebels in Syria |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427114815/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/08/world/middleeast/hezbollah-takes-risks-by-fighting-rebels-in-syria.html?_r=0 }}</ref>

5月8日，古賽爾爆發大規模戰鬥，同時間政府軍和地方人士也在進行調解，促使反對派撤出該城，但有許多士兵拒絕離開。<ref>[http://www.newser.com/article/da6569vo0/syrian-troops-push-into-strategic-town-on-highway-to-jordan-as-internet-outage-engulfs-country.html Syrian troops push into strategic town on highway to Jordan as Internet outage engulfs country]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>另外，一則未經證實的報導表示，真主黨部隊屠殺了30個試圖逃離開城的人，並將遺體帶走丟棄。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/09/world/middleeast/syria-diplomacy-kerry-aid.html |title=As Syria Diplomacy Gains, Kerry to Announce More Aid |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211064034/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/09/world/middleeast/syria-diplomacy-kerry-aid.html }}</ref>

5月9日，政府軍奪取鄰近古賽爾的許瑪雅（Shumariyeh），並向加山尼耶（Ghassaniyeh）進軍。另一方面，赫美爾被三枚砲彈攻擊，還有兩枚落在瑪查理艾奎。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/05/09/Syria-troops-Hezbollah-advancing-on-Qusayr-NGO-says.html |title=Syria troops, Hezbollah advancing on Qusayr, NGO says |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803234819/https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/05/09/Syria-troops-Hezbollah-advancing-on-Qusayr-NGO-says.html }}</ref>

5月10日，政府軍向城內民眾空投傳單，警告居民在攻擊前撤離，不過反對派人士否認有任何傳單出現。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/71132/World/Region/Syria-army-warns-civilians-to-leave-Qusayr-Militar.aspx |title=Syria army warns civilians to leave Qusayr: Military |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2021-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210232855/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/71132/World/Region/Syria-army-warns-civilians-to-leave-Qusayr-Militar.aspx }}</ref>然而，一名當地居民證實空投傳單的消息。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ewn.co.za/2013/05/10/Army-shelling-kills-25-in-Syria |title=Army shelling kills 25 in Syria |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008015609/https://ewn.co.za/2013/05/10/Army-shelling-kills-25-in-Syria }}</ref>真主黨則主要針對儲藏城內水資源的[[水缸|水缸]]和淨化場砲擊。<ref>[http://world.time.com/2013/05/10/un-rights-chief-alarmed-over-syrian-troop-buildup/ UN Rights Chief Alarmed over Syrian Troop Buildup]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>在當時，估計有25,000名平民留在城中。<ref name="Hezbollah in Q 2013">{{cite news | title=Hezbollah Aids Syrian Military In a Key Battle | date=2013-05-20 | agency=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] | accessdate=2013-05-20 | author=ANNE BARNARD and HWAIDA SAAD; Anne Barnard and Hwaida Saad reported from Beirut. Hala Droubi contributed reporting from Riyadh, Saudi Arabia}}</ref> 此外據報導，三名黎巴嫩籍士陣亡，還有36人不知去向。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2013/May-10/216606-3-lebanese-fighters-killed-in-syria-36-others-missing.ashx#axzz2Su4WYyOQ |title=3 Lebanese fighters killed in Syria, 36 others missing |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2018-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181105233720/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2013/May-10/216606-3-lebanese-fighters-killed-in-syria-36-others-missing.ashx#axzz2Su4WYyOQ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

5月11日，反對派收復阿比爾，藉此可緩解古賽爾和霍姆斯之間的軍事壓力。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/strategic-village-will-help-ease-rebels-movement |title=Strategic village will help ease rebels' movement. |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304074316/http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/strategic-village-will-help-ease-rebels-movement }}</ref>不過，政府軍於第二天即奪回。另外，政府軍打破了[[基督教|基督教]]派村莊加山尼耶的包圍網，該城已被反對派包圍長達八個月之久。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/nowsyrialatestnews/syria-christian-village-breathes-easier-as-army-advances |title=Syria Christian village breathes easier as army advances |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019082216/https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/nowsyrialatestnews/syria-christian-village-breathes-easier-as-army-advances }}</ref>

5月13日，政府軍攻下古賽爾北方的達明那艾加比耶（Damina al-Gharbiyah）、海達耶（Haidariyeh）和伊什艾瓦瓦（al-Warwar），使得反對派的運輸路線遭受威脅，也代表政府軍在抵達古賽爾，只剩下其他三個攻擊目標，包括上個月丟失的艾達巴空軍基地。政府軍已掌握古賽爾南方和東方的外圍地區，另外還有一個部隊從西方向此城前進。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jT0RGZgiJxBSeHl1Ldoqv8uU8ITw?docId=CNG.b736c800fa345dd0ed4b84ca0517bc60.2a1 |title=Abandoned arms as Syria rebels pull back near Qusayr |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2014-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315171530/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jT0RGZgiJxBSeHl1Ldoqv8uU8ITw?docId=CNG.b736c800fa345dd0ed4b84ca0517bc60.2a1 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/71362/World/Region/Syrian-army-takes-strategic-villages-near-Qusayr-O.aspx |title=Syrian army takes strategic villages near Qusayr: Officer |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004103158/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/71362/World/Region/Syrian-army-takes-strategic-villages-near-Qusayr-O.aspx }}</ref>

5月18日，叛軍在奧龍特斯河的敘利亞側，伏擊試圖從邊界進入敘利亞的真主黨份子，10人陣亡。隔天拂曉，一個新的真主黨部隊再向古賽爾進軍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/05/19/Hezbollah-fighters-head-to-strategic-Aleppo-town-as-fighting-rages-.html |title=Hezbollah fighters head to strategic Aleppo town as fighting rages |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427114902/https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/05/19/Hezbollah-fighters-head-to-strategic-Aleppo-town-as-fighting-rages-.html }}</ref>5月18日與5月19日的晚間，艾達巴空軍基地爆發大規模衝突，反對派和政府軍交戰，同時政府軍也轟炸反對派控制的村莊波伊達艾沙科雅（Boueida al-Sharqiya）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lorientlejour.com/article/815029/syrie-raids-aeriens-sur-la-ville-de-qousseir-.html |title=Syrie : raids aériens sur la ville de Qousseir |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427114905/https://www.lorientlejour.com/article/815029/syrie-raids-aeriens-sur-la-ville-de-qousseir-.html }}</ref>

=== 古賽爾戰鬥 ===
{{main|第二次古賽爾戰鬥}}

5月19日，在經過兩天的休整後，政府軍於早晨時動用軍機、大砲和迫擊砲轟炸古賽爾，並在稍晚時，由政府軍和數百名真主黨民兵的合作之下，從數個方向攻入城內。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syria-army-launches-assault-on-rebel-held-qusayr-ngo.aspx?pageID=238&nID=47139&NewsCatID=352 |title=Syria army launches assault on rebel-held Qusayr: NGO |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2017-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009230000/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syria-army-launches-assault-on-rebel-held-qusayr-ngo.aspx?pageID=238&nID=47139&NewsCatID=352 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22586378 |title=Syria army 'storms' rebel town Qusair |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2017-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205092935/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22586378 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/83563-syrian-observatory-military-pounds-rebel-town-of-qusayr-killing-13 |title=Syrian Observatory: Military Pounds Rebel Town of Qusayr, Killing 13 |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019073859/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/83563-syrian-observatory-military-pounds-rebel-town-of-qusayr-killing-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>總計當日白天城內外共有九個衝突地點。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.turkishweekly.net/news/150563/syrian-army-hezbollah-kill-over-30-in-border-town.html |title=Syrian army, Hezbollah kill over 30 in border town |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2014-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304144236/http://www.turkishweekly.net/news/150563/syrian-army-hezbollah-kill-over-30-in-border-town.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根據一位軍方消息人士透露，不久過後政府軍進入市中心，控制了中心廣場和市政大樓。<ref name="senior">{{Cite web |url=http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/168127 |title=Senior Hizbullah Official Killed in Syria Fighting |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2018-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181022033624/http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/168127 |dead-url=no }}</ref>一位反對派人士否認此說法，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.3news.co.nz/Syrian-troops-attack-rebel-town-30-dead/tabid/417/articleID/298362/Default.aspx |title=Syrian troops attack rebel town, 30 dead |access-date=2013-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328111801/http://www.3news.co.nz/Syrian-troops-attack-rebel-town-30-dead/tabid/417/articleID/298362/Default.aspx |archive-date=2014-03-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>但另名反對派人士證實政府軍奪取了市政大樓，並控制全城的六成地區。<ref name="key">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/20/world/middleeast/syrian-army-moves-to-rebel-held-qusayr.html?pagewanted=al&_r=0 |title=Hezbollah Aids Syrian Military in a Key Battle |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2016-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418041154/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/20/world/middleeast/syrian-army-moves-to-rebel-held-qusayr.html?pagewanted=al&_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

第二天，官方媒體則報導，政府軍已經平定城的東部地區，且仍於北區和東區掃蕩殘存份子。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2013/may/20/syria-crisis-battle-for-qusair |title=Syria crisis: battle for Qusair – live updates |access-date=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2013-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130708051613/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2013/may/20/syria-crisis-battle-for-qusair }}</ref>反對派也發出消息，表示戰鬥集中發生在城的北區部分。<ref name="lebanonborder"/>

SOHR則表示，儘管部分關於政府軍是否進城的報導有所衝突，但也證實有軍隊聚集在古賽爾的西方，以進行圍攻。從城北的空軍基地望向古賽爾，也可看見濃濃的黑煙，顯示戰鬥持續中，政府軍正在試圖奪回城內的設施。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2013/0520/Syrian-Army-Hezbollah-bear-down-on-rebels-in-strategic-Qusayr |title=Syrian Army, Hezbollah bear down on rebels in strategic Qusayr |access-date=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111232044/https://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2013/0520/Syrian-Army-Hezbollah-bear-down-on-rebels-in-strategic-Qusayr }}</ref>

另外，一名反對派人士表示，政府軍和真主黨成員已退卻回城的外圍一帶，而[[自由敘利亞軍|自由敘利亞軍]]（FSA）的發言人則說，政府軍意圖強攻入城，但成功被阻止。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gulfnews.com/in-focus/syria/qusayr-battle-claims-30-hezbollah-fighters-1.1186211 |title=Qusayr battle claims 30 Hezbollah fighters |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2013-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521122234/http://gulfnews.com/in-focus/syria/qusayr-battle-claims-30-hezbollah-fighters-1.1186211 |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過，另一名反對派人士重申，政府軍奪取了市政大樓和市中心，並且擊退大部分的反對派份子。<ref name="lebanonborder">{{Cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/05/20/23-hezbollah-fighters-reportedly-killed-in-syria-in-clashes-by-lebanon-border/ |title=28 Hezbollah fighters reportedly killed in Syria in clashes by Lebanon border |access-date=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924182553/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/05/20/23-hezbollah-fighters-reportedly-killed-in-syria-in-clashes-by-lebanon-border/ }}</ref>[[半島電視台|半島電視台]]駐[[貝魯特|貝魯特]]的一名記者也報導政府軍似乎已經控制古賽爾大部分地區。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/05/2013519124646578835.html |title=Syrian offensive on Qusayr deepens |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2014-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030131624/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/05/2013519124646578835.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

第三天，真主黨的精銳部隊再度從黎巴嫩越過邊界，前往古賽爾進行戰鬥。<ref name="newfighters">{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenewage.co.za/96503-1020-53-Hezbollah_sends_new_fighters_to_bloody_Syria_battle |title=Hezbollah sends new fighters to bloody Syria battle |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025145039/http://www.thenewage.co.za/96503-1020-53-Hezbollah_sends_new_fighters_to_bloody_Syria_battle |dead-url=no }}</ref>SOHR首次證實戰火已蔓延至城中，也報告了邊境村莊發生的衝突，造成兩名反對派份子陣亡，數人受傷。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/3-more-hezbollah-fighters-die-after-being-wounded-in-battle-for-key-syrian-town-activists-say/2013/05/21/9524a03e-c202-11e2-9642-a56177f1cdf7_story.html |title=Syrian army, Hezbollah fighters battle rebels in town near Lebanon border 3rd straight day |access-date=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2019-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115134552/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/3-more-hezbollah-fighters-die-after-being-wounded-in-battle-for-key-syrian-town-activists-say/2013/05/21/9524a03e-c202-11e2-9642-a56177f1cdf7_story.html }}</ref>

5月22日，[[敘利亞全國委員會|敘利亞全國委員會]]（SNC）主席{{link-en|喬治·薩布拉|George Sabra}}呼籲「每個擁有武器或彈藥的人都應將其送往古賽爾和霍姆斯，增加反對派的抵抗能力」。反對派軍隊「聯合旅」（Al-Tawheed Brigade）則派出30輛載著士兵的車隊，從[[阿勒頗|阿勒頗]]前往古賽爾，並在之後，聯合旅的Abu Firas宣稱他們也送出救護車、防空武器和彈藥。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aa.com.tr/en/politics/184261--tawhid-brigade-in-aleppo-sends-support-units-to-al-qusayr |title=Tawhid Brigade in Aleppo sends support units to al-Qusayr |access-date=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2015-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610085802/http://www.aa.com.tr/en/politics/184261--tawhid-brigade-in-aleppo-sends-support-units-to-al-qusayr }}</ref>然而，數日後反對派人士否認有任何支援抵達古賽爾，強調目前是自身作戰。<ref name="forcespush">{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/25/us-syria-crisis-qusair-idUSBRE94O05320130525 |title=Hezbollah, Syria government forces push for advance in Qusair |access-date=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924181541/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/25/us-syria-crisis-qusair-idUSBRE94O05320130525 }}</ref>一名反對派人士則表示政府軍和真主黨切斷了大多數的陸路運輸路線，其他人士並再次重申政府軍可能大約控制了城內六成地區，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/22/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE94L0EZ20130522 |title=Syria rebels call for reinforcements as war spreads abroad |access-date=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924181458/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/22/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE94L0EZ20130522 }}</ref>甚至官方還表示已佔領八成地區。<ref>[http://www.newsobserver.com/2013/05/22/2910249/syrian-opposition-urges-rebels.html Syrian opposition urges rebels to join key battle]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

政府軍謹慎地於城中掃蕩目標，其中重武器的戰鬥引致古賽爾遭到相當程度的破壞。之後，傳出恐怖組織[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]的指揮官Abu Omar陣亡的消息，使得政府軍士氣更加高昂。地面指揮官則指出，古賽爾的戰鬥還會持續一段時間，可能需要再一週收復反對派盤據的古賽爾北區，同時艾達巴空軍基地也尚由反對派所控制。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-qusayr-battle-far-over |title=Syria: Qusayr Battle Far From Over |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025145215/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-qusayr-battle-far-over |archive-date=2014-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

政府軍宣稱在首日的戰鬥中，有百名反對派份子喪生。<ref name="bastion">{{Cite web |url=http://www.rappler.com/world/29576-syrian-forces-storm-rebel-bastion-of-qusayr |title=Syrian forces storm rebel bastion of Qusayr |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207054558/https://www.rappler.com/world/29576-syrian-forces-storm-rebel-bastion-of-qusayr }}</ref>反對派組織SOHR則表示總計76名反對派份子、31名真主黨民兵、12名政府軍和8位平民於前三日戰鬥身亡。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/proche-orient/article/2013/05/22/l-armee-syrienne-libre-appelle-a-defendre-qoussair_3415196_3218.html|title=L'Armée syrienne libre appelle à défendre Qoussair|date=2013-05-22|accessdate=2013-05-23|publisher=[[Le_Monde|Le Monde]]|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427115055/https://www.lemonde.fr/proche-orient/article/2013/05/22/l-armee-syrienne-libre-appelle-a-defendre-qoussair_3415196_3218.html}}</ref>其他的反對派人士估計前兩日約90名反對派人士、<ref name="turningpoint">{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-turning-point-battle-qusayr |title=Syria: Turning Point in the Battle of Qusayr |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131209185655/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-turning-point-battle-qusayr |archive-date=2013-12-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>30名真主黨民兵及20名政府軍陣亡。一份黎巴嫩的資料則透露12至20名真主黨民兵戰死。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/20/us-syria-crisis-qusair-idUSBRE94J06520130520 |title=Thirty Hezbollah fighters killed in Syrian town: activists |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924181416/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/20/us-syria-crisis-qusair-idUSBRE94J06520130520 }}</ref><ref name="syriasqusayr">{{Cite web |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5h_k7MOo2uD4PRev5J9XKz9yLJkZA?docId=CNG.e94508b90db4f933086776e785c0f15e.aa1 |title=Hezbollah fighters killed in battle for Syria's Qusayr |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526084825/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5h_k7MOo2uD4PRev5J9XKz9yLJkZA?docId=CNG.e94508b90db4f933086776e785c0f15e.aa1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在第四日的戰鬥中，89位反對派份子陣亡，其中包括6名黎巴嫩人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=185961862 |title=Syrian Opposition Urges Rebels To Join Key Battle |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615215936/www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=185961862 |dead-url=no }}</ref>戰鬥進行至第五日時，真主黨的兵員損失已上升到46名。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.albawaba.com/news/hezbollah-suffers-heavy-losses-syrian-conflict-104-killed-according-watchdog-494039 |title=Hezbollah suffers heavy losses in Syrian conflict: 104 killed according to watchdog |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008001100/https://www.albawaba.com/news/hezbollah-suffers-heavy-losses-syrian-conflict-104-killed-according-watchdog-494039 }}</ref>

5月24日，根據報導，政府軍為了切斷古賽爾反對派僅存的補給路線，挺進鄰近村莊漢迪耶（Hamdiyeh）。<ref>[http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=186416002 Russia: Syrian Regime May Take Part In Peace Talks]</ref>一位軍方人士透露，反對派被圍困在由阿賈（Arjun）、艾達巴和古賽爾北區所組成的三角地帶，大批份子往艾達巴空軍基地退卻，而政府軍則採取穩紮穩打的攻勢，平定每個地區再推進。因為周邊道路由政府軍控制，反對派只獲得極少數的支援。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-army-tightens-grip-fighters-qusayr |title=Syria: Army Tightens Grip on Fighters in Qusayr |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025145826/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-army-tightens-grip-fighters-qusayr |archive-date=2014-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 

5月25日，軍方宣稱政府軍與真主黨從西北方打破艾達巴空軍基地的防線，已進入設施並正在交戰中。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syria-regime-takes-key-qusayr-objective-army-claims.aspx?pageID=517&nID=47586&NewsCatID=352 |title=Syria regime takes key Qusayr objective, army claims |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019072515/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syria-regime-takes-key-qusayr-objective-army-claims.aspx?pageID=517&nID=47586&NewsCatID=352 }}</ref>SOHR則表示戰鬥在空軍基地周圍進行，雖然政府軍發動轟炸，但是反對派仍保有空軍基地。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/agencia-efe/130525/syrian-opposition-45-lebanese-militants-killed-qusayr#13 |title=Syrian opposition: 45 Lebanese militants killed in Qusayr |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2014-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029060426/http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/agencia-efe/130525/syrian-opposition-45-lebanese-militants-killed-qusayr#13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

5月27日，經過戰鬥後漢迪耶落入政府軍與真主黨手中，緊接著政府軍為求完全包圍反對派，將茅頭轉移至哈雷特艾特庫曼（Haret al-Turkumen）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.enca.com/world/war-correspondent-gunned-down-syria |title=War correspondent gunned down in Syria |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019064013/http://www.enca.com/world/war-correspondent-gunned-down-syria |dead-url=no }}</ref>一名反對派人士透露，政府軍控制約三分之二的古賽爾城，而另名人士則表示，政府軍持續阻撓反對派的增援行動，增援的部隊試圖減輕古賽爾承受的攻擊，但卻在城的近郊受阻。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/52012033#.UaN6ZEBHIpk |title=Syria fighting rages amid reports of chemical attacks |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130611002132/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/52012033#.UaN6ZEBHIpk |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Syria-fighting-rages-amid-reports-of-chemical-attacks-314497 |title=Syria fighting rages amid reports of chemical attacks |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112025441/https://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Syria-fighting-rages-amid-reports-of-chemical-attacks-314497 }}</ref>此外，在真主黨據點赫美爾，一位黎巴嫩女性於反對派的砲擊下喪生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nst.com.my/latest/syria-opposition-rebels-cautious-on-eu-arms-decision-1.288388 |title=Syria opposition, rebels cautious on EU arms decision |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022014230/http://www.nst.com.my/latest/syria-opposition-rebels-cautious-on-eu-arms-decision-1.288388 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

5月29日，官方媒體報導政府軍在經過五個小時的戰鬥過後，成功奪取空軍基地，而真主黨相關媒體也播出相關影片，可發現坦克已被部署於基地內，且政府軍在飛機庫內走動。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/29/us-syria-crisis-dabaa-idUSBRE94S0ZO20130529 |title=Syrian army seizes strategic air base near Qusair: media |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924181649/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/29/us-syria-crisis-dabaa-idUSBRE94S0ZO20130529 }}</ref>政府軍則表示軍隊前進至艾達巴。<ref>[http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/breaking-news/elite-troops-in-pivotal-battle-for-qusayr/story-fn3dxix6-1226653389113 Elite troops in pivotal battle for Qusayr]</ref>隔日，SOHR和法魯克旅的一名女發言人也證實空軍基地失守的消息。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://supportkurds.org/news/thursday-30-may-2013/ |title=Thursday 30 May 2013 |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615215927/http://supportkurds.org/news/thursday-30-may-2013/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="setback">{{Cite web |url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2013/05/29/3422918/hezbollah-said-to-control-most.html |title=Hezbollah said to control most of Qusayr in major setback for Syria rebels |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2014-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202121237/http://www.miamiherald.com/2013/05/29/3422918/hezbollah-said-to-control-most.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

5月30日，政府軍攻陷位於古賽爾西北方六公里的村莊阿賈，阻斷反對派經由此處撤退的機會。<ref>[http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/world/352644/syria-opposition-snubs-peace-talks-offer Syria rebels boosted as Assad forces close in]</ref><ref name>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22728798 |title=Syria conflict: Rebel reinforcements arrive in Qusair |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111224929/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22728798 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.trust.org/item/20130531185534-obuwv/?source=hpagehead |title=Assad forces advance; West, Russia exchange barbs ahead of talks |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025145612/http://www.trust.org/item/20130531185534-obuwv/?source=hpagehead }}</ref>同日，300名反對派份子從夏姆西（Shamsinn）打破防線，當中有11人陣亡。儘管如此，反對派人士表示城內的處境還是相當險峻，正處在寡不敵眾及無法負荷攻勢的情形，若西方國家繼續未提供支援，可能會戰敗。<ref name="ferocious">{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/06/20136193221742616.html |title=Qusayr rebels face ferocious assault |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427115241/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/06/20136193221742616.html }}</ref>

5月31日，政府軍攻佔賈瓦迪耶（Jawadiyeh），等同於切斷古賽爾所有聯外出入口，並加強圍攻行動。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=187465776 |title=Balance Of Power In Syria Shifting Assad's Way |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615215924/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=187465776 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Jun-01/219124-regime-rebels-bolster-forces-for-qusayr-battle.ashx#axzz2Uy9Kl3F9 |title=Regime, rebels bolster forces for Qusayr battle |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211011634/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Jun-01/219124-regime-rebels-bolster-forces-for-qusayr-battle.ashx#axzz2Uy9Kl3F9 }}</ref>

6月5日，敘利亞官方媒體報導政府軍控制了古賽爾全城，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/06/2013655429874831.html |title=Syria 'regains control' of stragetic Qusayr |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806221038/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/06/2013655429874831.html }}</ref>反對派份子則表示已經退出該城。一名真主黨民兵透露經過整夜的迅速攻勢，迫使一些反對派撤退。一則新聞指出政府軍正在北邊進行掃蕩，而據報導反對派退守部分依然控制住的艾達巴。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/05/us-syria-crisis-town-idUSBRE95406220130605|title=Syrian army captures strategic border town of Qusair|publisher=Reuters|date=5 June 2013|accessdate=5 June 2013|archive-date=2015-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151011094130/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/05/us-syria-crisis-town-idUSBRE95406220130605}}</ref>

在戰鬥中，總計反對派約1,900名份子，超過500名陣亡，1,000名負傷，<ref name="lose"/>而根據反對派來源，真主黨損失70–110人，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2013/0605/Hezbollah-marks-major-triumph-as-Qusayr-tips-back-into-Assad-camp?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+feeds%2Fcsm+(Christian+Science+Monitor+%7C+All+Stories) |title=Hezbollah marks major triumph as Qusayr tips back into Assad camp |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2019-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205020156/https://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2013/0605/Hezbollah-marks-major-triumph-as-Qusayr-tips-back-into-Assad-camp?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+feeds%2Fcsm+(Christian+Science+Monitor+%7C+All+Stories) }}</ref>真主黨人士則認為至少100人喪生，政府軍方則未知死傷人數。<ref name="setback"/>

=== 掃蕩行動 ===
6月6日，政府軍對最多反對派聚集的布瓦達（Buwaydah）進行轟炸，另外也有部分反對派份子留在古賽爾和艾達巴一帶的果園。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/73339/World/Region/Syria-army-pounds-village-near-Qusayr-Watchdog.aspx |title=Syria army pounds village near Qusayr: Watchdog |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028035335/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/73339/World/Region/Syria-army-pounds-village-near-Qusayr-Watchdog.aspx }}</ref>當日稍晚，政府軍奪取艾達巴。<ref name="keepup">{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/rebels-attack-air-base-in-northern-syria-days-after-regime-captured-strategic-town/2013/06/07/27b6e994-cf54-11e2-8573-3baeea6a2647_story.html |title=Syrian troops, Hezbollah fighters keep up offensive, capture 2 central villages |accessdate=2013-06-15 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615220041/www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/rebels-attack-air-base-in-northern-syria-days-after-regime-captured-strategic-town/2013/06/07/27b6e994-cf54-11e2-8573-3baeea6a2647_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/06/06/307523/syrian-troops-recapture-another-town/ |title=<nowiki>Syrian Army troops take full control of al-Daba’a town</nowiki> |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924132756/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/06/06/307523/syrian-troops-recapture-another-town/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

隔日，SOHR表示艾達巴外圍仍有戰鬥進行，而布瓦達持續遭到轟炸。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://au.news.yahoo.com/latest/a/-/latest/17520427/syria-forces-seek-to-capitalise-on-qusayr-victory/ |title=SYRIA FORCES SEEK TO CAPITALISE ON QUSAYR VICTORY |accessdate=2013-06-15 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615215915/au.news.yahoo.com/latest/a/-/latest/17520427/syria-forces-seek-to-capitalise-on-qusayr-victory/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>另外，至少十數名古賽爾的難民在政府軍砲擊果園時喪生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/07/world/middleeast/syrian-forces-pursue-insurgents-who-fled-fallen-town.html?_r=0 |title=Syrian Forces Chase Rebels Who Fled Fallen Town |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008210515/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/07/world/middleeast/syrian-forces-pursue-insurgents-who-fled-fallen-town.html?_r=0 }}</ref>之後，政府軍再攻下薩西耶（Salhiyeh）和馬紹迪耶（Masoudiyeh）兩座村莊，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=189441551 |title=Syrian Troops Capture Central Villages |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607162201/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=189441551 |dead-url=no }}</ref>並向布瓦達推進。根據官方媒體報導，晚間政府軍攻入布瓦達，追擊反對派份子，<ref name="keepup"/>政府軍則宣稱已佔領布瓦達<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/06/07/307693/syria-army-retakes-villages-near-qusayr/ |title=Syria Army retakes three villages near Qusayr |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607211937/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/06/07/307693/syria-army-retakes-villages-near-qusayr/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>但未被證實。

6月8日，布瓦達被政府軍攻陷，也代表整個古賽爾地區已經進入政府軍的控制之下。反對派在最後戰鬥上損失慘重，數十名份子被俘虜，其中包括部分外國戰鬥者。<ref name="final">{{Cite web |url=http://www.saudigazette.com.sa/index.cfm?method=home.regcon&contentid=20130608169028 |title=Syrian forces capture final rebel stronghold in Qusair region |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2014-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030201010/http://www.saudigazette.com.sa/index.cfm?method=home.regcon&contentid=20130608169028 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sunherald.com/2013/06/08/4720407/car-bomb-explodes-in-central-syrian.html |title=Car bomb explodes in central Syrian city |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-06-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615215910/http://www.sunherald.com/2013/06/08/4720407/car-bomb-explodes-in-central-syrian.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>反對派表示，政府軍在古賽爾附近果園，對一個約2,000人的難民群攻擊，其中包括反對派份子和平民，反對派女發言人表示有110位平民喪生，包括40位婦孺和20位反對派份子。<ref name="#1"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=190724245 |title=Syrian Rebels Reeling From Loss Of Qusair |access-date=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130611203440/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=190724245 }}</ref>

== 戰略分析 ==
此次進攻古賽爾的目的，主要歸類有三種。第一，建立從[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]通往[[地中海|地中海]]沿岸的通道，此處為[[阿拉維派|阿拉維派]]大本營，因此可藉此奠定基礎。第二，確保撤離路線，若政府軍放棄大馬士革，可往海岸地區撤退。第三，保護與霍姆斯的輸送路線，以對霍姆斯進行最終攻擊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenational.ae/thenationalconversation/comment/al-assad-is-looking-to-his-future |title=Al Assad is looking to his future |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193417/http://www.thenational.ae/thenationalconversation/comment/al-assad-is-looking-to-his-future }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mininggazette.com/page/content.detail/id/309991/Syrian-regime-shoring-up-hold-on-capital--coast-.html?isap=1&nav=5016 |title=Syrian regime shoring up hold on capital, coast |access-date=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2013-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513121554/http://www.mininggazette.com/page/content.detail/id/309991/Syrian-regime-shoring-up-hold-on-capital--coast-.html?isap=1&nav=5016 }}</ref>，而該城正好位於運輸路線的咽喉。<ref name="Hezbollah in Q 2013"/>

